lead_paragraph: The rowing and canoeing venue for the 2020 Olympics should either be moved to a site hundreds of miles (kilometers) away in northern Japan or downgraded to a temporary facility in Tokyo, a city government cost-cutting panel said Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Tokyo Panel Details Venue Changes, Cost Cuts for 2020 Games
headline.main: Tokyo Panel Details Venue Changes, Cost Cuts for 2020 Games
